&lt;li&gt;Architect and build a robust, scalable and stable infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and build Infrastructure that is easily maintainable during patching and upgrades without downtime&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and build Infrastructure with AWS regional level failure tolerance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work together with our Security Engineers to provision a secure Infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automations for AWS Deployments to ensure fast delivery of Cloud Services to our developers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide through Automations means for developers to easily deploy resources on AWS&lt;/li&gt;
