&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://speakerdeck.com/paypaycorporation/6deed4120e21c6e72efdbff49ea3c077&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;PayPay 5 senses&lt;/a&gt;に当てはまる方&lt;/li&gt;
