&lt;h3&gt;About the Organization/Team・組織/チームについて&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team you will join primarily leads projects related to the renewal of our banking systems. Our in-house engineers take the lead in driving initiatives from scratch — from initial planning and design through to hands-on coding. As a newly established team, you will have the unique opportunity to help shape our development standards and build the engineering environment together from the ground up.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;※ After joining the company, you are expected to be seconded to PayPay Bank as a member of the above project.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
