&lt;h2 class=&quot;col-sm-9 col-12 content&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About PayPay&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-9 col-12 content&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PayPay is a FinTech company that has grown to over 70M (as of July 2025) users since its launch in 2018. Our team is hugely diverse with members from over 50 different countries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OUR VISION IS UNLIMITED_ &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We dare to believe that we do not need a clear vision to create a future beyond our imagination. PayPay will always stay true to our roots and realize a vision (future) that no one else can imagine by constantly taking risks and challenging ourselves. With this mindset, you will be presented with new and exciting opportunities on a daily basis and have the opportunity to grow and reach new dimensions that you could never have imagined. We are looking for people who can embrace this challenge, refresh the product at breakneck speed and promote PayPay with professionalism and passion.&lt;br&gt;※ Please note that you cannot apply or be selected in parallel with PayPay Corporation, PayPay Card Corporation and PayPay Securities Corporation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2018年にサービスを開始してから約7年でユーザー数7000万人を突破したフィンテック企業であるPayPayは約50か国の国と地域から集まった多様なメンバーで構成されています。&lt;/p&gt;
